call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Graham's (CHA) pass to Wanamaker (CHA) goes out of bounds.
Bridges (CHA) jumps vertically contesting the driving shot attempt by Bogdanovic (ATL) and he absorbs the contact.
Bridges (CHA) places a hand on Capela's (ATL) back and marginal contact occurs during his shot attempt at the basket.
Goodwin (ATL) moves alongside of Wanamaker (CHA) and marginal contact occurs during his drive to the basket.
Rozier (CHA) extends an arm into Goodwin's (ATL) path when he sets the screen and affects his ability to defend the play.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor that the ball is last touched by Rozier (CHA) before going out of bounds stands.
Bridges (CHA) reaches in and makes contact to Goodwin's (ATL) arm/body that affects his SQBR.
Graham (CHA) legally contests Bogdanovic's (ATL) jump shot attempt.
Hill (ATL) legally contests Rozier's (CHA) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Rozier (CHA) extends his leg and initiates contact with Hill (ATL) that causes him to lose his balance as he contests the jump shot attempt.
McDaniels (CHA) commits a take foul on Bogdanovic (ATL).
